729201f-a.title: Richmond: New Dorp Lane - Clawson Street
729201f-a.text:
(1)
New Dorp Lane, north side, between Clawson and Edison Streets,
showing the D. L. Clawson House. Butler's 1853 map and Beers's
1874 and 1887 maps show it to have belonged to the above family.
The real estate atlases from 1898 to 1917 show it to be the
property of D.J. Tysen.
April 1925
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
(2)
The same, another view.
April 1925
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
